d clearing his mind involves using both cognitive and environmental strategies to create a focused and uncluttered mental state. By blocking out external distractions such as sunlight and using a rapid mental scanning technique to clear false associations, Jorj can ensure that he is well-rested, alert, and mentally prepared for the challenges of his space mission.">
